Package edu.brown.cs.mramesh4.TripGraph

Class CityNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.mramesh4.TripGraph.CityNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TripGraphNode<CityNode,​CityEdge>
    public class CityNode
extends Object
implements TripGraphNode<CityNode,​CityEdge>
    This is a class to model our CityNodes: CityNodes are nodes that represent a point on our Graph. Each point on the graph can calculate distances between other cities as well as store information about itself.
